# Default page template (RIIFT)

The default Shopify page template is [`templates/page.json`](../../templates/page.json). It must use **`riift-page-content`**, not Horizon `main-page`.

## Rules

- Do **not** reintroduce `main-page` or other Horizon page sections into `page.json`.
- Interior marketing pages use **Default page** in Admin — there is no separate `page.riift.json` alternate.
- If Horizon layout is needed for an edge case, use the **`page.horizon`** alternate template only.

## Alternates (intentional)

| Template file | Admin label | Use |
|---------------|-------------|-----|
| `page.json` | Default page | RIIFT interior pages (Claude HTML) |
| `page.contact.json` | contact | RIIFT contact form |
| `page.wizard.json` | wizard | RIIFT wizard |
| `page.styleguide.json` | styleguide | Dev styleguide |
| `page.horizon.json` | horizon | Horizon escape hatch |

See [`_docs/PAGE_BUILD_GUIDE.md`](../../_docs/PAGE_BUILD_GUIDE.md).
